author: Brady Renard
title: Asics McNeese Cowboy Stampede set for October 3
text:
Asics McNeese Cowboy Stampede set for October 3 Posted: SOURCE: McNeese State Sports Information Department Men’s 4-Mile College Junior Varsity / Middle school 2-mile LAKE CHARLES, LA (KPLC) - 
The 10th Annual ASICS McNeese Cowboy Stampede will take place at the Chennault Airpark, where 51 University and High School Teams are entered to compete. Events kick off with the University Women's race. 
7:00 a.m. - Course Inspection8:30 a.m. - Women’s 5k College9:15 a.m. - Men’s 4 Mile College9:45 a.m. - Varsity Girls 5K10:15 a.m. - Varsity Boys 5K10:45 a.m. - Junior Varsity / Middle school Girls 2 mile11:15 a.m. - Junior Varsity / Middle School Boys 2 mile12:00 a.m. - Awards University Teams Scheduled to Compete: McNeese, ULL, SELA, NWST, Nicholls, Grambling, Southern-BR, Loyola-NO & Texas Southern High Schools Sch eduled to Compete : Schools from the five parish area, Lafayette and Southeast TX will be represented.Results Will be Live courtesy of AdkinsTrak Meet Central and can be found here .
